title: 218: Surprise Rookies & Super Sophomores
itunes:title: 218: Surprise Rookies & Super Sophomores
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks list their rookies (9:49) and second year players (16:15) that have stepped up so far this season. The guys also break down their games of the week (00:53) before they make a few bold predictions (22:24). DJ and Bucky wrap the show by picking the biggest college football match ups (29:34).
